Plot domain object

Source: R/sdtm_domain.R
plot.domain.Rd

Plot domain object

Usage

# S3 method for class 'domain'
plot(
  x,
  testcd = NULL,
  points = TRUE,
  lines = FALSE,
  legend = TRUE,
  color = NULL,
  ...
)

Arguments

x

A domain object.

testcd

Testcd field to filter for, defaults to all if NULL.

points

Plot points, as logical.

lines

Plot lines, as logical.

legend

Plot legend, as logical.

color

Field to color points and lines by.

...

Further parameters.

Value

A ggplot2 object.

Examples

plot(domain(examplinib_sad, "lb"))
